\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你post自己打丁裸照先再撐啦"},{"pid":"902a68e3c78d7ae4f0743674ccf54d01189e1759","tid":2517350,"uid":7050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"之前有個巴打寫咗劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a83e08be8955e12f3eb1702f9fe1bbe723cf117","tid":2517350,"uid":200681,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"已經預示到聽日東張西望會點回應朱凌凌流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2513669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2513669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a86de60f342b032c4ee33542e93608c492790e66","tid":2517350,"uid":47954,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">一。首先會搵吳幸美電話訪問朱凌凌</span></ins></strong><br />\n吳幸美：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朱凌凌：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳：「你依家停曬工係咩心情？」<br />\n朱：「依家已經無咩事，報左警等警察處理。係自己年少貪玩，亦都信錯人，但無諗過會咁。知道自己作為公眾人物，愛回家都有好多小朋友觀眾，會影響到佢地，想講聲唔好意思，以後都會成熟啲，唔會再犯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">二。金城安單獨訪問（鮮有地好嚴肅咁）</span></ins></strong><br />\n旁白：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金城安：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旁白：「今日朱凌凌停工無參與拍攝，愛回家劇組又點睇呢？」<br />\n金：「都無特別去問佢呢啲事，俾啲空間佢，佢成年人黎相信佢會handle到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><ins>三。愛回家劇組接受訪問</ins></strong></span><br />\n旁白：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長腳蟹：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n湯盈盈：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劉丹：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豹哥：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旁白：「至於愛回家其他一眾演員，都一樣好支持朱凌凌呀！」<br />\n成班人：「無事！哈哈！好小事啫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n長腳蟹：「好支持佢！好小事啫，邊個後生仔無貪玩過吖！」<br />\n劉丹：「我地全部都好支持佢嘅，呢啲小風波好快就會過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n（成班人企埋一邊陰陰咀笑住聽）<br />\n<br />\n隔左陣之後豹哥入鏡，成班人指住豹哥：「呢啲片佢以前拍得仲多啦！」「係囉！咩都睇過曬添！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n豹哥：「哈哈！係囉！我以前都拍唔少，好小事姐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（哈哈大笑一輪扮正經）不過呢，大個仔啦，唔好再犯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"16766aa2284aa9a4311e5fc992cea3f9d1500667","tid":2517350,"uid":386968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:09:03.000Z","msg":"如果係viutv的後生咁做，tvb的人會點講？"},{"pid":"16a6ab934be67898cc912d71120cbc9095ddd1dc","tid":2517350,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a65250b9e4e608ca6753c1802f117c0f872299c","tid":2517350,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"劉丹今天（5日）出席TVB處境喜劇《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》宣傳母親節活動，談到母親節，丹爺覺得很好笑，每年這個節日都會有人送花給他：「好奇怪，有時候我送花畀人，又有人會送花畀我，但都係一個開心節日。」<br />\n<br />\n近日TVB藝人吳偉豪不雅影片流出，外界有種種傳聞，有傳因此事會被TVB雪藏，甚至會被踢出劇集《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》，丹爺都知道有這件事情發生，力撐吳偉豪沒有錯：「我成日都講一句，朱凌凌（吳偉豪）根本冇做錯，只不過係交友不慎。同埋講真呀，我哋都後生過，成日都想問吓年輕人自己有冇做過呀，都冇人夠膽話冇，咁咪係囉，大家都知咩事，只不過佢唔好彩。大家講啲鼓勵說話，將事情慢慢丟淡佢，然後再重新投入工作。」<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210505/466628911342555136791350.jpeg/blnA3ERGZwFbRdNL1Q3oEvhRS0cDGtJnqygpk6soKZM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210505%2F466628911342555136791350.jpeg%2FblnA3ERGZwFbRdNL1Q3oEvhRS0cDGtJnqygpk6soKZM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=bef77793&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦無人想知，成日開埋依d post搶頭香咁好威威咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 