oji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><ins>三。愛回家劇組接受訪問</ins></strong></span><br />\n旁白：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長腳蟹：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n湯盈盈：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劉丹：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豹哥：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旁白：「至於愛回家其他一眾演員，都一樣好支持朱凌凌呀！」<br />\n成班人：「無事！哈哈！好小事啫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n長腳蟹：「好支持佢！好小事啫，邊個後生仔無貪玩過吖！」<br />\n劉丹：「我地全部都好支持佢嘅，呢啲小風波好快就會過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n（成班人企埋一邊陰陰咀笑住聽）<br />\n<br />\n隔左陣之後豹哥入鏡，成班人指住豹哥：「呢啲片佢以前拍得仲多啦！」「係囉！咩都睇過曬添！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n豹哥：「哈哈！係囉！我以前都拍唔少，好小事姐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（哈哈大笑一輪扮正經）不過呢，大個仔啦，唔好再犯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"好有畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3954f062b1aa684f98e7d0ea9b8d58ae32eb16f7","tid":2517350,"uid":256393,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5mvmim.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5mvmim.png&h=553d6213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6491962db6dff079301f7e47f685ecde3c73e1f","tid":2517350,"uid":331264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"18e8f3852d429f43983e07683cac2b6894cc38fb","tid":2517350,"uid":268516,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"最錯係碌鳩咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"